name: bonkwifhat
description: Bonkwihat is inspired by the two largest solana memecoins. $BIF was launched on February 29, 2024, as the perfect combination of Bonk and Dogwifhat. As a fully decentralized memecoin, $BIF has 0% tax, its liquidity is burnt (locked for eternity), and mint authority was revoked at launch, making it a coin by and for the people. The main goal of BIF is to follow the path of these inspirations and become a top memecoin of the solana blockchain
